      "date": "2014-11-20 17:13:31.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review-1\n\n<4>Lustre: DEBUG MARKER: == lustre-rsync-test test complete, duration 1605 sec == 15:05:47 (1415977547)\n<4>Lustre: DEBUG MARKER: running=$(grep -c /mnt/lustre' ' /proc/mounts);\n<4>if [ $running -ne 0 ] ; then\n<4>echo Stopping client $(hostname) /mnt/lustre opts:-f;\n<4>lsof /mnt/lustre || need_kill=no;\n<4>if [ x-f != x -a x$need_kill != xno ]; then\n<4>    pids=$(lsof -t /mnt/lustre | sort -u);\n<4>   \n<4>Lustre: setting import lustre-MDT0000_UUID INACTIVE by administrator request\n<3>LustreError: 28411:0:(file.c:184:ll_close_inode_openhandle()) lustre-clilmv-ffff88007a3a4000: inode [0x200000002:0x2:0x0] mdc close failed: rc = -108\n<3>LustreError: 28411:0:(client.c:2353:__ptlrpc_req_finished()) dereferencing freed request (bug 575)\n<0>LustreError: 28411:0:(client.c:2354:__ptlrpc_req_finished()) LBUG\n<4>Pid: 28411, comm: umount\n<4>\n<4>Call Trace:\n<4> [<ffffffffa0634895>] libcfs_debug_dumpstack+0x55/0x80 [libcfs]\n<4> [<ffffffffa0634e97>] lbug_with_loc+0x47/0xb0 [libcfs]\n<4> [<ffffffffa09907e7>] __ptlrpc_req_finished+0x557/0x6d0 [ptlrpc]\n<4> [<ffffffffa0991200>] ptlrpc_req_finished+0x10/0x20 [ptlrpc]\n<4> [<ffffffffa11caf7d>] ll_close_inode_openhandle+0x5dd/0x10b0 [lustre]\n<4> [<ffffffffa11cbe0c>] ll_md_real_close+0x1ac/0x220 [lustre]\n<4> [<ffffffffa11fe495>] ll_md_blocking_ast+0x3c5/0x7f0 [lustre]\n<4> [<ffffffffa0965c5c>] ldlm_cancel_callback+0x6c/0x170 [ptlrpc]\n<4> [<ffffffffa09784ca>] ldlm_cli_cancel_local+0x8a/0x470 [ptlrpc]\n<4> [<ffffffffa097d0f0>] ldlm_cli_cancel+0x60/0x360 [ptlrpc]\n<4> [<ffffffffa0971dfd>] cleanup_resource+0x1bd/0x360 [ptlrpc]\n<4> [<ffffffffa064b28e>] ? cfs_hash_spin_lock+0xe/0x10 [libcfs]\n<4> [<ffffffffa0971fcf>] ldlm_resource_clean+0x2f/0x60 [ptlrpc]\n<4> [<ffffffffa064b50c>] cfs_hash_for_each_relax+0x17c/0x350 [libcfs]\n<4> [<ffffffffa0971fa0>] ? ldlm_resource_clean+0x0/0x60 [ptlrpc]\n<4> [<ffffffffa0971fa0>] ? ldlm_resource_clean+0x0/0x60 [ptlrpc]\n<4> [<ffffffffa064ce5f>] cfs_hash_for_each_nolock+0x7f/0x1c0 [libcfs]\n<4> [<ffffffffa096ef4e>] ldlm_namespace_cleanup+0x2e/0xc0 [ptlrpc]\n<4> [<ffffffffa106df09>] mdc_import_event+0x1e9/0xa30 [mdc]\n<4> [<ffffffffa09bc7cd>] ptlrpc_invalidate_import+0x2dd/0x8c0 [ptlrpc]\n<4> [<ffffffffa06451a1>] ? libcfs_debug_msg+0x41/0x50 [libcfs]\n<4> [<ffffffffa099a558>] ptlrpc_set_import_active+0x3d8/0x670 [ptlrpc]\n<4> [<ffffffffa1069f52>] mdc_iocontrol+0x2402/0x2690 [mdc]\n<4> [<ffffffff8103f9d8>] ? pvclock_clocksource_read+0x58/0xd0\n<4> [<ffffffff8128ceb6>] ? vsnprintf+0x336/0x5e0\n<4> [<ffffffffa0e1a30a>] lmv_iocontrol+0x28a/0x2b80 [lmv]\n<4> [<ffffffffa0644b73>] ? libcfs_debug_vmsg2+0x5d3/0xbc0 [libcfs]\n<4> [<ffffffff8119b502>] ? user_path_at+0x62/0xa0\n<4> [<ffffffffa06451a1>] ? libcfs_debug_msg+0x41/0x50 [libcfs]\n<4> [<ffffffff8116f503>] ? kmem_cache_alloc_trace+0x1a3/0x1b0\n<4> [<ffffffffa11e373d>] ll_umount_begin+0x1fd/0xbc0 [lustre]\n<4> [<ffffffff811ac00a>] sys_umount+0x11a/0x3a0\n<4> [<ffffffff8118eb34>] ? sys_newstat+0x24/0x50\n<4> [<ffffffff810e1e07>] ? audit_syscall_entry+0x1d7/0x200\n<4> [<ffffffff8100b072>] system_call_fastpath+0x16/0x1b",
